---
title: Baja Fish Tacos with Crunchy Red Cabbage Slaw
description: Flaky white fish is coated in a smoky Cajun spice to make a delicious fish taco! The crunchy radish and cabbage slaw add a heaping helping of fibre-rich veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-de-poisson-de-style-baja-16f3a2d4.jpg
